quote.p:
Noted and discussed an oral briefing by the Director of Central
                            Intelligence on the subject, with specific reference to a summary of the
                                UN report on the Hungarian uprisings;
                            the recent publications of the official text of Mao Tse-tung’s speech of February 1957;
                            the Chinese Communist troop withdrawals from Tibet; and the situations
                            in Indonesia, Thailand and the Middle East.
